metadata.name: Rev X #1
metadata.description: Rev X is a 2,222 supply project focussed on providing extensive utility/value to holders whilst also being the hottest PFP in the space. They give you access to a community with a valuable suite of NFT-related tools, frequent and successful alpha calls, upcoming marketplace to purchase WL spots, NFTs and more. As well as this utility, we have a tight-knit, active and knowledgable discord community (access via NFT) focused on helping each other stay up-to-date with the market and providing as much value as possible.
